Package com.six.timapi

Class TransactionResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.six.timapi.TransactionResponse
  • public class TransactionResponse
extends Object
    Contains the result of a transaction finished after calling Terminal.transaction(com.six.timapi.constants.TransactionType, com.six.timapi.Amount) or Terminal.transactionAsync(com.six.timapi.constants.TransactionType, com.six.timapi.Amount). Immutable class.
